**Coffee 4 Bitcoin** is an online retailer offering Capulin brand coffee from Nayarit Mexico.

This ecommerce site is among the first online shopping sites offering goods in exchange for bitcoins.

Though the business name is Coffee 4 Bitcoin, the URL has those two inverted.

